 ('114', '274', 'en_us', 'Mark Arigoni', NULL, NULL, '<p>Mark is a Principal of Milone &amp; MacBroom and is the Regional Manager of the firm’s Massachusetts office. He is responsible for the project development and management of design, coordination, specifications, cost estimates, construction documents, and permit applications for various projects located throughout New England. Project assignments have included the design of greenways, streetscapes, passive and active parks, environmental restorations, recreational facilities, athletic facilities, urban redevelopment and revitalizations, and commercial site developments. These projects have included several environmental restoration components such as brownfield redevelopment design, dam removal design, dam bypass channel design, and river restoration/fish passage design.</p>', '<p>Graduating with a B.S. in Landscape Architecture from the University of Connecticut, Mark is a licensed Landscape Architect in Connecticut, Massachusetts, and Maine. In addition, Mark is a member of the following professional organizations:</p>\n<ul><li><p>Council of Landscape Architectural Registration Board (CLARB)</p></li><li><p>Connecticut Board of Landscape Architects 2015-Present</p></li><li><p>Committee on Nominations CLARB, 2016-Present</p></li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '2017-07-26 19:42:07', '2017-07-31 13:13:19', '086d7c39-b3e2-4502-866b-f12106ddeddf'),
