 ('252', '913', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'What we faced. ', '<p>A wonderfully passionate community was in dire need of safer and more adequate athletic facilities at their High School Athletic Complex. What existed was an outdated, unsafe, undersized, and unuseable track and bleacher system, non-accessible and inadequate restroom, concessions, and storage facilities. The inadequate number of tennis courts in need of repair and an overall inefficient and unsafe layout of conflicting field and sport uses.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '2017-07-31 19:29:34', '2017-07-31 19:54:48', '491a703e-4b90-4e42-8290-99e26c59926c'),
 ('253', '914', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'right', NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '2017-07-31 19:29:34', '2017-07-31 19:54:48', '21243e75-235c-4e51-99a2-52f0123db783'),
 ('254', '915', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Including Passionate Stakeholders in the Master Planning Process ', '<p>Although with every design project the actual details for construction are extremely important to the success of the project,  perhaps equally important is the early involvement of the stakeholders in the concept stages of the project.   Our goal of the masterplanning process was to engage with the Track Committee and the users of the facility, the coaches, the booster club, the players, and the maintenance and facilities staff.  Only after having an informed ideas of what the stakeholders envision, could we put our designer hats on and begin the design and concept planning.  By having periodic check-ins and presentations with the stakeholders during our concept design phases, it made the “buy-in” of the project design a much smoother and cost effective process as the plans and specifications advanced through to bid documents..  The success of the project was our design team\'s ability to create a balance between the the long wish list of stakeholder desires,  and the real constraints of the project budget. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '2017-07-31 19:29:34', '2017-07-31 19:54:48', 'eb805995-2de4-4867-b18b-c1e4c9303474'),
 ('255', '916', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'left', 'The work in-progress ', '<p>Due the size of the project and the inclusion of the complete renovation of the the Boys &amp; Girls locker and team room facilities internal to the school, the project was required to follow the MGL Chapter 149 bidding requirements. This bidding procedure was lead by the MMI design team and led to a project that was completed within budget. </p>\n<p>The resulting athletic facility is a true testament to a collaborative design process. Collaborative not only in the sense of our engineers, planners and landscape architects, but a true collaboration between design team and the community.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '2017-07-31 19:29:34', '2017-07-31 19:54:48', '492830fb-10d6-4e3a-bed9-bb8b82b47141'),
