 ('910', 'field', '3', 'en_us', ' a wonderfully passionate community was in dire need of safer and more adequate athletic facilities at their high school athletic complex what existed was an outdated unsafe undersized and unuseable track and bleacher system non accessible and inadequate restroom concessions and storage facilities the inadequate number of tennis courts in need of repair and an overall inefficient and unsafe layout of conflicting field and sport uses what we faced 0 concept site plan concept gateway right although with every design project the actual details for construction are extremely important to the success of the project perhaps equally important is the early involvement of the stakeholders in the concept stages of the project our goal of the masterplanning process was to engage with the track committee and the users of the facility the coaches the booster club the players and the maintenance and facilities staff only after having an informed ideas of what the stakeholders envision could we put our designer hats on and begin the design and concept planning by having periodic check ins and presentations with the stakeholders during our concept design phases it made the buy in of the project design a much smoother and cost effective process as the plans and specifications advanced through to bid documents the success of the project was our design team s ability to create a balance between the the long wish list of stakeholder desires and the real constraints of the project budget including passionate stakeholders in the master planning process due the size of the project and the inclusion of the complete renovation of the the boys girls locker and team room facilities internal to the school the project was required to follow the mgl chapter 149 bidding requirements this bidding procedure was lead by the mmi design team and led to a project that was completed within budget the resulting athletic facility is a true testament to a collaborative design process collaborative not only in the sense of our engineers planners and landscape architects but a true collaboration between design team and the community the work in progress img 3459 left sample caption here img 6096 worthingtonimages com 2017 rt sample caption here img 5849 worthingtonimages com 2017 rt sample caption here img 5629 worthingtonimages com 2017 rt sample caption here mp 4218 worthingtonimages com 2017 rt a look at the finished product 1 a list of facility improvements include 0 0 new boys girls locker rooms new ticketing concession restroom satellite trainers room and three bay storage facility new 6 post tensioned concrete tennis courts with basketball accommodations new 6 lane 8 straight synthetic track new full size synthetic turf field with new field lighting system new 1500 seat bleacher system new stadium scoreboard and sound system new girls softball field dugouts and scoreboard section of new town bikeway access to facility new accessible parking renovated two story press box new baseball field dugouts fencing batting cage and scoreboard restored historical field signage archway decorative site lighting new multi use natural grass athletic fields and irrigation meet the team involved joanne samson practice lead mark arigoni practice lead agawam high school athletic facility renovation the gunnery athletic fields redesign related projects '),
